搭<br />\n真假波蘿-&gt;真假新聞<br />\n同依家差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ade751991d70880f28d1b26a3739212eeefca6","tid":1516374,"uid":168567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"如果唔成功 20年後既教科書<br />\n歷史:<br />\n2019年夏 <br />\n一班暴徒<br />\n破壞社會安寧"},{"pid":"8844874c6a1966b12ce80eedf7387494cb95c349","tid":1516374,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96ade751991d70880f28d1b26a3739212eeefca6","tid":1516374,"uid":168567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"如果唔成功 20年後既教科書<br />\n歷史:<br />\n2019年夏 <br />\n一班暴徒<br />\n破壞社會安寧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"贏左就己亥革命<br />\n輸左就一九暴動"},{"pid":"4d7f413c23f24cca13024ef7e1a520533cd4cef2","tid":1516374,"uid":290468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"唔好講笑，輸左唔係變左仔咁簡單，係變巴勒斯坦人，代代為奴，所以唔輸得，只可以贏，用幾耐時間，去都幾盡都要贏"},{"pid":"cbb8ff0b313a68a7cc81bae20d45ac4b26dcaa66","tid":1516374,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d2274181c4d8e42f6e604a2950fa43fd9cccd70","tid":1516374,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:24:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8a37376c293cff5eb9f9df24f5f2825f738d610b","tid":1516374,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:36:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fef0d044b802157abe3382f1a9a0230b41f9ff3","tid":1516374,"uid":259736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:38:48.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"3ba47125c54790dd4f6749ecce6148e5b36c7374","tid":1516374,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:40:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">謹言慎行</span> 呢四隻字好緊要"},{"pid":"bf6d13c34488c2a5d0599a2737750b7c896672ac","tid":1516374,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"758a0965d6fde389bbb675544994ce64b9a5b946","tid":1516374,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">【懶人包】</span></span></strong><br />\n左仔行動失去民意基礎，大部分市民支持港英維持秩序<br />\n六七暴動後，左仔沉左二十年，九七後先翻身<br />\n六七暴動，大家只記得燒死林彬、真假菠蘿陣炸死小朋友<br />\n港英警隊濫權濫捕無人會再記得，摩星嶺無人識<br />\n<br />\n憤怒但要保持理智，不要重覆六七暴動左仔嘅錯誤<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每一步行動都要思考對民意嘅影響。不割蓆，要檢討</span></strong><br />\n否則輸左之後，無人會再記得義士死傷、狗嘅濫權濫捕、新屋嶺etc....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武為劍 和理為盾<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 不捉鬼 不譴責<br />\nBe Water Be Humble<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">【引文】</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 行動升級，發動左派大罷工，雖然一度令食品出現短缺，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>卻反令中下層市民首當其衝，無法吸納市民支持</strong></span>，更令數以千計參與罷工的工人和公務員被解僱，行動盲目升級，卻埋下日後全面潰敗的伏線。<br />\n<br />\n2. 左派只顧把行動不斷升級，後來更放置<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真假菠蘿陣導致人心徨徨</span></strong>，英國政府一面取得發動輿論攻勢，甚至讓鄉事派也站在他們那邊，另一方面進行鐵腕鎮壓，成功平定暴動，更令<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">左派一沉不起，直至九十年代才逐漸走回台前</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3. 六七暴動迫使上層精英靠攏港英當局，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">追求生活安定的一般市民也在別無選擇的情況下，逐漸認同殖民地政府的管治</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n4. 六七暴動的腥風血雨，進一步加深香港人固有的恐共情結，港人對中國政府的不信任長期存在，即使回歸後仍未消除。港英政府利用鎮壓左派的機會，開始實施「洗腦贏心」(winning the hearts and minds)工程。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">徹底改變了香港人的深層意識和心理結構，形成了港人對『左派』、『共產黨』、『大陸』、『社會主義』的極度恐懼心理</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n5. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大部分港人對左派陣營的過激行徑感到不滿</span></strong>。暴動因而強化左派與香港主流社會長期存在的隔膜，左派自暴動結束後覺得被港英和主流社會抹黑，長期陷入自我孤立的狀態，並產生「被圍困」的心態(siege mentality)和受害者情結。暴動以失敗告終後，左派工聯會轉以內務為主，不參與社會事務，杯葛勞工顧問委員會等港英勞工諮詢架構，也沒有派員參與八二年舉行的首屆區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">【參考資料】</span></span></strong><br />\n六七暴動：香港戰後歷史的分水嶺 (引言)<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/recall-hk/67-3bd0a4c58604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Frecall-hk%2F67-3bd0a4c58604&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=c955b474\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/recall-hk/67-3bd0a4c58604</a><br />\n暴動與勇武： 讀張家偉 《六七暴動 &mdash; 香港戰後歷史的分水嶺》<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%88%87%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6-%E8%AE%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%AE%B6%E5%81%89-%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%83%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%B0%E5%BE%8C%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%B0%B4%E5%B6%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25AE%2580%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2581%2589-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B6%25BA%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=8d57aa0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25AE%2580%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2581%2589-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B6%25BA%2F&h=be874a93\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%88%87%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6-%E8%AE%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%AE%B6%E5%81%89-%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%83%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%B0%E5%BE%8C%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%B0%B4%E5%B6%BA/</a><br />\n「不割蓆，會檢討」喺抗爭必勝方程式 -  <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488459</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:41:17.000Z","msg":"唔係20年，係沉咗40年，當年班左仔學生，就係今日果班藍絲廢老"},{"pid":"49f33bc74f0f2d0a65f820c5e80d336819c85e0a","tid":1516374,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:42:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1分29秒速龍衝入鐵見人就打 到1分40秒佢啲伙計渴班速龍出嚟 入去做乜</span>由此可見本身落鐵拉人係唔預呢一part發生 去到最後同721冇分別</span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以大家一定要集中火力追擊831黑警恐襲太子站旺角站</span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvIau2kwxzZA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=5134e8b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n另外好重要好重要好重要<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aoLoCBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaoLoCBH.png&h=99a60b07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynKAtJo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynKAtJo.png&h=73eded90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e75e2fa3a4206d807290e00c86a83ef24424e8e","tid":1516374,"uid":123115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:44:20.000Z","msg":"如果我地今次輸左<br />\n就會係玩抖音班人 二三十年後嘅黃絲廢老<br />\n只許勝不許敗<br />\n<br />\n其實林奠一定了解 67<br />\n佢一定係想我地走番67後路從而收我地皮"}]}